                    <invention-title lang="en">Location-based advertising</invention-title>
                </bibliographic-data>
                <abstract lang="en">
                    <p>A first request for information that is related to a specified location is received. A first query for advertisements related to the specified location is submitted. A response to the first query that includes one or more advertisements related to the specified location is received. At least one of the one or more advertisements related to the specified location is sent to a client device. A second query for the information based on the first request is submitted. A first search result that is responsive to the second query is received. Information that is related to the location based on the first search result is sent to the client device after sending at least one of the one or more advertisements to the client device.</p>
